------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* ChessBase allows invalid e.p. squares, we will ignore the e.p. rights
silently in such cases.

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Scidb 1.0 BETA (rev. #661)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Severe bug in class BlockFile fixed.

* Modified the .scg file structure a bit: now time tables will be used for all
types of move info starting with first ply.

* Configure script changed: now inotify with syscall interface will be used if
Linux kernel is >= 2.6.13.

* Added "Copy this game to clipbase", "Paste last Clipbase game", and
"Paste game" to game bar.

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Scidb 1.0 BETA (rev. #656)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* CBF decoder enhanced; now tested with more than 1860 databases. Our decoder
now can decode games which even ChessBase (cb3.exe) cannot decode correctly;
one example is game #288 from
<ftp://ftp.pitt.edu/group/student-activities/chess/PGN/Players/kburg-pg.zip>.

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
