------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Broken linker hack again - another workaround. I decided to switch this hack
on per default. All newer versions of the GNU linker are broken.

* Game editor now shows some special annotation for the following states:
- "3x" if threefold repetition is detected (this will be flagged only one
  time)
- "50" if the fifty move rule is reached (every time the count is 50)

